Conditional Means

Notes:

library("dplyr")
## Warning: package 'dplyr' was built under R version 3.2.2
## 
## Attaching package: 'dplyr'

pf.fc_by_age <- pf %>%
  group_by(age) %>%
  summarise(friend_count_mean = mean(friend_count), 
            friend_count_median = median(friend_count),
            n = n()
            ) %>%
  arrange(age)

Create your plot!

ggplot(aes(x = age, y = friend_count_mean), data = pf.fc_by_age)+
  geom_line()

Overlaying Summaries with Raw Data

Notes:

ggplot(aes(x=age,y=friend_count),data=pf)+
  geom_point(alpha = 1/10, position = position_jitter(h = 0),color = "red")+
  coord_trans(y = "sqrt")+
  ylab("Friend Count")+
  xlab("Age")+
  geom_line(stat = "summary", fun.y = mean)+
  geom_line(stat = "summary", fun.y = quantile, prob = 0.1, linetype = 2,      color = "blue")+
  geom_line(stat = "summary", fun.y = quantile, prob = 0.9, linetype = 2,      color = "blue")+
  geom_line(stat = "summary", fun.y = quantile, prob = 0.5, color = "blue")

#+
#  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(30,60))




ggplot(aes(x=age,y=friend_count),data=pf)+
  geom_point(alpha = 1/10, position = position_jitter(h = 0),color = "#A52A2A")+
  ylab("Friend Count")+
  xlab("Age")+
  geom_line(stat = "summary", fun.y = mean)+
  geom_line(stat = "summary", fun.y = quantile, prob = 0.1, linetype = 2,      color = "blue")+
  geom_line(stat = "summary", fun.y = quantile, prob = 0.9, linetype = 2,      color = "blue")+
  geom_line(stat = "summary", fun.y = quantile, prob = 0.5, color = "blue")+
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(13,70), ylim = c(0,1000))

Understanding Noise: Age to Age Months

Notes:

pf$age_with_months <- pf$age + (12-pf$dob_month)/12

# 
library(dplyr)  

pf.fc_by_age_months <- pf %>%
    group_by(age_with_months)%>%
    summarise(friend_count_mean = mean(friend_count),
      friend_count_median = median(friend_count),
      n = n()
    ) %>%
    arrange(age_with_months)
    

p1 <- ggplot(aes(x = age, y = friend_count_mean), data = subset(pf.fc_by_age, age < 71))+
  geom_line(color = "blue" )+geom_smooth()

p2 <- ggplot(aes(x = age_with_months, y = friend_count_mean), data = subset(pf.fc_by_age_months, age_with_months < 71))+
  geom_line(color = "blue" )+geom_smooth()

p3 <- ggplot(aes(x = round(age/5)*5, y = friend_count_mean), data = subset(pf.fc_by_age, age < 71))+
  geom_line(color = "blue", stat = "summary", fun.y = mean )


library(gridExtra)
## Warning: package 'gridExtra' was built under R version 3.2.2
grid.arrange(p2,p1,p3,ncol=1)
